import React from 'react';

const Logo = ({ size = 40, className = '' }) => {
  return (
    <svg 
      width={size} 
      height={size} 
      viewBox="0 0 40 40" 
      fill="none" 
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      className={className}
    >
      <circle 
        cx="20" 
        cy="20" 
        r="18" 
        fill="url(#gradient)" 
        stroke="white" 
        strokeWidth="2"
      />
      <path 
        d="M12 16l8 6 8-6" 
        stroke="white" 
        strokeWidth="2.5" 
        strokeLinecap="round" 
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      />
      <path 
        d="M12 22l8 6 8-6" 
        stroke="white" 
        strokeWidth="2" 
        strokeLinecap="round" 
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      />
      <circle 
        cx="20" 
        cy="12" 
        r="2" 
        fill="white"
      />
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#4facfe"/>
          <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#00f2fe"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#667eea"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default Logo;
